# Real-world Data Project - Retail Sales Analysis

## Objective
Analyze a real-world retail sales dataset to uncover patterns, trends, and influencing factors.

## Technologies Used
- Python
- Pandas
- Matplotlib
- Seaborn
- Google Colab

## Tasks Performed
- Data exploration
- Data cleaning
- Statistical analysis
- Visualization of sales trends
- Correlation analysis

## Visualizations
- Weekly Sales Distribution
- Temperature vs Sales
- Fuel Price vs Sales
- Correlation Heatmap

## Key Insights
- Sales distribution patterns were identified.
- Temperature and fuel prices showed relationships with sales trends.
- Correlation analysis helped identify influencing factors.

## Outcome
Learned how to apply data science techniques in a real-world retail business scenario.
